      <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="verticalLayout_27">
       <item>
        <widget class="QLabel" name="label_17">
         <property name="text">
          <string>Global Hotkeys in Pub-Xel

Global Hotkeys allows opening files while Pub-Xel is running in the background. By default, Pub-Xel uses Alt+Shift+k, Alt+Shift+j, and Alt+Shift+p, which are chosen to minimize hotkey conflicts with other software.

You can enable and customize your hotkeys here. 
Combinations of Ctrl, Alt, Shift, and alphabets (a~z) are allowed.
</string>
